Resample many times to get sample distribution

set.seed(25) 

boot_dist_donor &lt;- organ_donor |&gt;
  specify(response = outcome, success = "complication") |&gt;
  generate(reps = 1000, type = "bootstrap") |&gt;
  calculate(stat = "prop")

