Next, we combine our two death rates to account for age using these proportions.

vaccine_age_outcome_perc |&gt;
  mutate(perc_wt = if_else(age == "50+", perc * 0.115, perc * 0.885)) |&gt;
  group_by(vaccine) |&gt;
  summarize(perc = sum(perc_wt))

# A tibble: 2 × 2
  vaccine       perc
  &lt;chr&gt;        &lt;dbl&gt;
1 Unvaccinated 0.712
2 Vaccinated   0.211








